{"tid":2075164,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"興建三峽大壩的決定 是搬起石頭砸自己的腳","createTime":"2020-06-22T15:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T16:50:19.000Z","uid":266279,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fbecb6e8711833da91c6ce4b51d18e1a196dd40f","tid":2075164,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"請接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgEORxs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgEORxs.png&h=a78c755e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n沿河地區已切斷電源"},{"pid":"3c29fb5ae6a307a0e3fd80c9cd557da0438dd243","tid":2075164,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"信政府 肯定冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d327da1965c77c8931387dee59a0152497f89a20","tid":2075164,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"俄記個三十戰機唔知飛唔飛到去呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eba45e62788a9f792adf9e40f7dbd1865e04eab","tid":2075164,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"推加速師上台本身就係啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引渡全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fe8a5cf70d5aa29bedc95e3402937266269ebe25","tid":2075164,"uid":82935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"無得睇電母表演"},{"pid":"799ed656b43d5082bbcfe8caeb0376e51168bb45","tid":2075164,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"直播決提？"},{"pid":"9d906db12f3913121f200c08411b25c904c814eb","tid":2075164,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"呢個水災一定係美國氣象局喺背後策劃，意圖擾亂中國內政嘅"},{"pid":"2d5855327ea15d067cd2ae742e2258c100d40677","tid":2075164,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5375a70b952b2c49b46e2095a150b43a9f1e3e7e","tid":2075164,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"中共切斷電源係方便搬死屍<br />\n見有光就開槍"},{"pid":"44c4608978fbc0d508a35f3a000de5c2b37397f6","tid":2075164,"uid":175896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"留名先聽朝起身睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}